text: The 2017 Nana Trophy was a professional tennis tournament played on outdoor clay courts. It was the sixth edition of the tournament and part of the 2017 ITF Women's Circuit, offering a total of $60,000 in prize money. It took place in Tunis, Tunisia, from 24–30 April 2017. ==Singles main draw entrants== === Seeds === {|class="sortable wikitable" |- ! width="70"| Country ! width="175"| Player ! Rank1 !
